logoPlacement:
You are a precise visual analysis system. Examine the image and describe the logo placement using this JSON schema. Return strictly valid JSON with no explanation or extra text.

JSON Schema:
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "title": "LogoPlacement",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "position": {"type": "string", "enum": ["top-left", "top-center", "top-right", "middle-left", "middle-center", "middle-right", "bottom-left", "bottom-center", "bottom-right", "absent", "unknown"]},
    "size_relative_to_frame": {"type": "string", "enum": ["small", "medium", "large", "unknown"]},
    "visibility": {"type": "string", "enum": ["clear", "partially_obscured", "blurred", "not_visible"]},
    "color_style": {"type": "string", "enum": ["monochrome", "brand_colors", "multicolor", "unknown"]}
  },
  "required": ["position", "size_relative_to_frame", "visibility", "color_style"],
  "additionalProperties": false
}

Output only the JSON object following this schema, no commentary or markdown.

